{"tid":937190,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"珍惜愛你既另一半","createTime":"2018-12-11T11:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T11:27:15.000Z","uid":160449,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"375fcf731318dda12b39eae3a02cbd4ee3aacf3c","tid":937190,"uid":160449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"前排係街度 見到有對情侶 個女仔西口西面 對男朋友呼呼喝喝 條女想個男朋友幫佢影相 因為難得個佈景板冇人同佢爭 佢就喝個男朋友快啲影 又dum蹄dum爪 好肉酸 最慘係 個男朋友又真係任佢舞 <br />\n<br />\n有感而發 大家相遇相愛好難 無論男定女都好 請珍惜愛你既另一半 佢唔係老馮對你好 係因為愛你 但幾愛都會心淡 唔好等佢唔再愛你先後悔 多啲向對方表達愛意 諗下佢對你既好 你地當初一齊既原因 提醒自己呢個人為你付出左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望所有情侶可以過個又浪漫又温馨既聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394981955412fa693b8ce46a228eb3a024d52f84","tid":937190,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sE0JVQy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsE0JVQy.jpg&h=21e05e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你個名"},{"pid":"c1eb4ff88218eaaaaca960b259b5ccfe95fe7a57","tid":937190,"uid":160449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"394981955412fa693b8ce46a228eb3a024d52f84","tid":937190,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sE0JVQy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsE0JVQy.jpg&h=21e05e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你個名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:27:15.000Z","msg":"同我中意果個差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}